OK, what's Angry Birds Stars?

00:07:03.520 --> 00:07:05.408
AUDIENCE: There is no
such thing as Stars.

00:07:05.408 --> 00:07:06.830
Star Wars, maybe?

00:07:06.830 --> 00:07:08.269
ADE OSHINEYE: See, I'm confused.

00:07:08.269 --> 00:07:09.810
My point is, when
I go to google.com,

00:07:09.810 --> 00:07:13.340
I'm going to type Angry Birds
Stars, and it's going to say,

00:07:13.340 --> 00:07:14.590
you didn't mean that.

00:07:14.590 --> 00:07:16.400
You meant Angry Birds Star Wars.

00:07:16.400 --> 00:07:18.410
But my friend told
me Angry Birds Stars,

00:07:18.410 --> 00:07:19.660
and who am I going to believe?

00:07:19.660 --> 00:07:22.190
You or the guy in the pub?

00:07:22.190 --> 00:07:24.310
So if you're going
to be in search,

00:07:24.310 --> 00:07:25.820
you've got to be
thinking, how do I

00:07:25.820 --> 00:07:27.950
make sure I rank for my name?

00:07:27.950 --> 00:07:31.000
How do I rank for common
misspellings of my name?

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:33.230
Because again,
your users probably

00:07:33.230 --> 00:07:36.560
don't spend their time obsessing
about the latest releases

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:41.224
you've done, even if you are as
famous as the Angry Birds guys.

00:07:41.224 --> 00:07:42.515
They even have branded hoodies.

00:07:44.789 --> 00:07:46.330
First thing you've
got to be thinking

00:07:46.330 --> 00:07:48.666
is, are you doing a
good job with SEO?

00:07:48.666 --> 00:07:50.340
Do you have a
website for your game

00:07:50.340 --> 00:07:53.190
where people can actually
discover you through search?

00:07:53.190 --> 00:07:56.230
One of the best ones in the
world, the Play Store search

00:07:56.230 --> 00:07:58.880
is not as good as
google.com's search.

00:07:58.880 --> 00:08:02.470
It's getting better, but this
is still one of the best places

00:08:02.470 --> 00:08:03.959
to get discovered.

00:08:03.959 --> 00:08:06.250
So obviously you can do things
like have a Google+ page

00:08:06.250 --> 00:08:08.730
to make it easier for them
to discover your brand

00:08:08.730 --> 00:08:11.590
or your game.

00:08:11.590 --> 00:08:14.440
But again, it means that when
they type your name in or they

00:08:14.440 --> 00:08:17.680
type a horrible misspelling
of your name-- for example,

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:20.940
