00:08:20.940 --> 00:08:22.260
Again, as a user, I don't care.

00:08:22.260 --> 00:08:24.660
I just type some
approximation to search,

00:08:24.660 --> 00:08:27.030
and search points me
in the right direction.

00:08:33.940 --> 00:08:36.289
The point is, search-- and
of course, advertising--

00:08:36.289 --> 00:08:39.530
are great ways to let
people get maximum reach.

00:08:39.530 --> 00:08:41.929
They are ways where
people can discover you.

00:08:41.929 --> 00:08:43.720
So they've discovered you.

00:08:43.720 --> 00:08:46.320
Now this could mean they've
discovered you through the Play

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:47.840
Store, or it could mean
they've discovered you

00:08:47.840 --> 00:08:49.341
because they went
to your website.

00:08:49.341 --> 00:08:51.340
And of course, you have
a link to the Play Store

00:08:51.340 --> 00:08:52.589
so they can install your game.

00:08:52.589 --> 00:08:54.322
OK Yes?

