00:09:00.280 --> 00:09:02.710
Because that's embarrassing.

00:09:02.710 --> 00:09:04.630
All right, so the
user's found you.

00:09:04.630 --> 00:09:06.052
You need to convert them.

00:09:06.052 --> 00:09:08.510
So conversion could be as simple
as they click on the link,

00:09:08.510 --> 00:09:09.990
they get taken to
the Play Store.

00:09:09.990 --> 00:09:10.780
Great.

00:09:10.780 --> 00:09:14.550
If you've got a game that spans
multiple platforms or spans

00:09:14.550 --> 00:09:17.150
the web, and Android
and iOS, as well,

00:09:17.150 --> 00:09:19.990
one of things we have with
