00:09:19.990 --> 00:09:22.320
where they can
sign in on the web,

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:25.030
and then we can push
the app, the game,

00:09:25.030 --> 00:09:28.850
to their devices over the air
so that you can convert them

00:09:28.850 --> 00:09:34.040
on the web, and they've got the
game installed on their device.

00:09:34.040 --> 00:09:38.930
The point is, if the user signs
in on the web or on Android,

00:09:38.930 --> 00:09:40.610
they should be
signed in everywhere.

00:09:40.610 --> 00:09:43.535
That means when
