I sign in.

00:09:54.950 --> 00:09:56.860
I should resume from
where I started,

00:09:56.860 --> 00:10:00.230
from where I was last
time on my other devices.

00:10:00.230 --> 00:10:03.610
So I shouldn't have to worry
about every time starting again

00:10:03.610 --> 00:10:04.560
from scratch.

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:06.360
So when we think
about conversion,

00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:08.620
conversion could be as
simple as getting the user

00:10:08.620 --> 00:10:11.100
