They need the money.

00:16:00.440 --> 00:16:03.720
So everybody does this, or
if they're not doing this,

00:16:03.720 --> 00:16:05.730
they're thinking
about doing this.

00:16:05.730 --> 00:16:08.680
And the reason they do this
is because a person plays

00:16:08.680 --> 00:16:11.480
the game, they get a certain
way in, they get bored

00:16:11.480 --> 00:16:14.680
or they get stuck,
and they stop playing.

00:16:14.680 --> 00:16:16.040
How do we re-engage them?

00:16:16.040 --> 00:16:17.590
Well, you nag them.

00:16:17.590 --> 00:16:18.400
You spam them.

00:16:18.400 --> 00:16:20.520
And you hope they come back.

00:16:20.520 --> 00:16:22.910
Does it work on you guys?

00:16:22.910 --> 00:16:25.940
Who here actually gets
a re-engagement email,

00:16:25.940 --> 00:16:27.610
they get a re-engagement
notification,

00:16:27.610 --> 00:16:29.776
and then they say, oh well,
